spec_data.Name: perl-inc-latest
spec_data.Description:
The inc::latest module helps bootstrap configure-time dependencies for CPAN
distributions. These dependencies get bundled into the inc directory within
a distribution and are used by Makefile.PL or Build.PL.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 06:50:49 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Use modules bundled in inc/ if they are newer than installed ones
